word_group.brief_definition: 自立性；有独立的存在性

bilingual.source: He believes in the existence of God.
I believe in the existence of true love.
Existentialism often explores the meaning of life and human existence.
bilingual.target: 存在主义经常探讨生命和人类存在的意义。

bilingual.source: Do you believe in the existence of flying saucers?
Hume questioned the existence of innate ideas.
bilingual.target: 休谟质疑天赋观念的存在。

bilingual.source: Many people believe in the existence of spirits.
bilingual.target: 很多人相信鬼神的存在。

bilingual.source: He does not believe in the existence of a werewolf.
Do you believe in the existence of Santa Claus?
bilingual.target: 你相信圣诞老人的存在吗？

bilingual.source: The book explores the ontology of human existence.
bilingual.target: 这本书探讨了人类存在的本体论。

bilingual.source: Many people are unaware of the existence of the pangolin.
bilingual.target: 许多人不知道穿山甲的存在。

list.abstract: 《Existence》是歌手sim在2016年4月7日发行专辑《the beautiful people》中的歌曲。

yingyinNormal.en: So what proof do we have of its existence?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们该如何印证车子的存在？

yingyinNormal.en: I don't understand. Their existence is conditional?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不明白，卧室的存在有条件的吗？

yingyinNormal.en: These Infinity Stones each control an essential aspect of existence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些无限宝石每一颗都控制一种存在的必要方面。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you think the animal is contemplating its own existence?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你认为她是在刷存在感吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I wasn't even aware of its existence until yesterday. I'm not talking about its existence. I'm talking about what it depicts.
yingyinNormal.zh: 到昨天为止我都不知道它的存在。我不是问录像的存在，我是问里面的内容。

yingyinNormal.en: Why hast thou forsaken me, O deity whose existence I doubt?
yingyinNormal.zh: 神啊，我一直怀疑你的存在，你为何抛弃我？

yingyinNormal.en: Making their master happy was the tribe's very reason for existence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小黄人种族存在的意义就是为了让他们的主人开心。

yingyinNormal.en: Why did you bring me here? To find out who you told of our existence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你为什么要带我来这？想了解你把我们的存在告诉了谁。

yingyinNormal.en: It gives proof to the existence of matter. Without time, we don't exist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 时间才是唯一的测量单位，没有时间，我们就不存在。

yingyinNormal.en: Time gives legitimacy to its existence. Time is the only true unit of measure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 时间就是存在的证明，时间才是唯一的测量单位。

yingyinNormal.en: We've codified our existence to bring it down to human size to make it comprehensible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们把自己的存在加以简化以方便人类理解。

yingyinNormal.en: Under no circumstances can he be made aware of my existence. You must promise me this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他决不能知道我的存在，你要向我保证这一点。

yingyinNormal.en: Despite the risks of this collective existence, many species use the reef as a nursery.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尽管这种集体生活存在风险，很多物种还是将珊瑚礁作为了栖息地。

yingyinNormal.en: The Expansion the reason for my very existence would be over, so I did what I had to do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个扩张计划我存在的理由将毁于一旦，所以我做了我该做的事儿。

yingyinNormal.en: Humans consider themselves unique, so they rooted their whole theory of existence on their uniqueness.
yingyinNormal.zh: 人类总以为自己是独特的，存在理论总是以独特性为基础。

yingyinNormal.en: Everything that lives around us suffers from our existence. We leave footprints everywhere we go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 身边的一切都因为我们的存在而遭受痛苦，我们所到之处都留下脚印。

yingyinNormal.en: Their very existence is a threat. Is that clear, Commander? Clear, sir. Good. Carry on, Colonel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们的存在就是个威胁，明白吗，指挥官？明白，很好，请继续，上校。

yingyinNormal.en: No, but your ability to perceive their existence is conditional on you passing the second and third barriers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，但对你来说卧室的存在是有条件的，你要通过第二和第三关。

yingyinNormal.en: We're talking about a being whose very existence challenges our own sense of priority in the universe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们现在在讨论的这个人，他的存在挑战了我们自身对事物优先级别的认知。

yingyinNormal.en: So, how you been? Well, my existence is a continuum, so I've been what I am at each point in the implied time period.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你最近怎样？我的存在是个连续统一体，所以在指定期间的每个时间点都是一样的。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: n. 存在；生存；实体；生活；存在物
adj. 存在的；现存的；现行的；目前的

word_family.mean: v. 存在；实际上有；生存；生活；被发现

sense_info_list.en: a way of living especially when this is difficult or boring

examination_example.sentence: Beethoven's music tends to move from chaos to order as if order were an imperative of human <highlight>existence</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 贝多芬的音乐往往从混乱变得有序，好像秩序对人类的存在是极为重要的。

examination_example.sentence: For him, order does not result from forgetting or ignoring the disorders that plague our <highlight>existence</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于他而言，忘记或忽略那些困扰人类生存的混乱并不能换来秩序。

examination_example.sentence: But we are now knowledgeable enough to reduce many of the risks that threatened the <highlight>existence</highlight> of earlier humans.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但我们现在有足够的知识来减少许多威胁早期人类生存的风险。

sense_info_list.en: the fact or state of living or having objective reality
